title_full:
aya featuring Iceboy Violet

              —
              Emley lights us moor
            
              (Hyperdub)
label: Hyperdub
description:
Two of the NW/Yorkshire’s breakthru stars team up on a standout from AYA’s superb ‘im hole’ album, already bound for AOTY 2021 listings.

Minting their very own style of mutant drill/grime/wot da fuck u want to call it, ‘Emley lights us moor’ contrasts their voices between an especially quiet start from AYA, and harder bars from Iceboy, innovating in the interstices between known styles and conventions. Lowkey genius this; think Tricky meets Mykki on a faded and slanted one at Arca’s gaff.
